N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 368.9 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) There shall be
no fee charged for: (1)
inspection of
records; (2)
search for records; or
(3)
any certification pursuant
to this Part. (b) The
fee for photocopies of records shall be 25 cents per page, not exceeding 9 by
14 inches. Notes
